==反響==
《深夜加油站遇見蘇格拉底》獲得的評價褒貶不一。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據73篇評論，新鮮度25%，平均得分為4.7 / 10，但觀眾的新鮮度達76%<ref>{{rotten-tomatoes|peaceful_warrior|Peaceful Warrior}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分40，好壞平均參雜<ref>{{metacritic film|peaceful-warrior|Peaceful Warrior}}</ref>。《[[芝加哥太陽報|芝加哥太陽報]]》的知名評論家[[羅傑·伊伯特|羅傑·伊伯特]]給了電影2.5星的評價（滿分4星）<ref>{{cite web|title=''Peaceful Warrior'' :: rogerebert.com :: Reviews|url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20060622/REVIEWS/60517004|work=[[Roger_Ebert|Roger Ebert]]|publisher=''[[Chicago_Sun-Times|Chicago Sun-Times]]''|date=2006-06-23|accessdate=2012-10-21|archive-date=2009-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090604102856/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20060622%2FREVIEWS%2F60517004|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

